steps.name: I Login
I click on New Application Link
I select YES for Are you currently studying at school or college in the UK?
I select United Kingdom - England as UK School Country
I select School from the drop down list
I select "Y1" answer for Which UK Year Group are you in?
I enter all Teacher Details
I save & go to "Parents/Guardian" tab
I complete Parent/Guardian Form and save it
I select "Pathways to Medicine" as my course
I select start date as "12/03/2018"
I select strand as "Design Engineering"
I select FSM as "No"
I select House hold income as "0 - 25000"
I select care as "No"
I select Carer as "No"
I select parent guardian education as "Yes" and save the form
I enter my personal statement as "This is my personal stateme"
I select my Data Policy & Marketing as "Email"
I accept terms & conditions and save the form
I click On "Review
I click on "Submit Application" buton
I should get successful message "Thank you for submitting your application"
